Horn Clause Form

<Exp>      ::= <rule> |
               <query>
<rule>     ::= <atom> |                        
               <atom> <= <literals>           
<query>    ::= ? <literals>                    
<literal>  ::= atom | not <atom>
<literals> ::= <literal> [and <literals>]
<atom>     ::= <predicate_ident> [ ( <terms> ) ]            
<term>     ::= <ident> ( <terms> )  | <constant> | <variable>
<terms>    ::= <term> [, <terms>]
